Santander’s Villalabeitia Departs as Head of Loan Distribution

-- B y   P a t r i c i a   K u o
-- 
2011-08-01T11:54:59Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-01/santander-s-villalabeitia-departs-as-head-of-loan-distribution.html
Gregorio Villalabeitia, head of
European loan distribution in  London  at  Banco Santander SA (SAN) , has
left the bank, said a spokeswoman for the lender, who declined
to be identified in line with company policy.  Santander,  Spain ’s biggest bank, is the top syndicated loan
arranger in Spain and  Portugal , with a 10.5 percent share of the
39.5 billion euros ($57 billion) of issuance this year,
according to data compiled by Bloomberg.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Patricia Kuo in London at 
